        <body>
      
		<pb n="1"/>
			<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Richmond</placeName> Erab <add>&#63;</add>.H. <date>5612</date></p>
			<p><addressee>Rev Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">Esteemed Friend&#33;</p>
          <p rend="indent(3)">Your last kind favour<lb/> came duly to hand&#44; and&#44; its contents noted&#44;<lb/> and would have replied on its receipt<lb/> had it have been urgent&#44; but I supposed<lb/> that my silence indicated to you that we<lb/> would defer the publication of the testimony.<lb/> I wish that it were in my power to pay the<lb/> <sic>the</sic> <sic>expence</sic> of this printing myself I can assure<lb/> you I would do so. I am disgusted at<lb/> the proceedings of the German congregation&#44; it<lb/> is without exception the most irreligious<lb/> proceeding I ever heard of&#44; the case I am<lb/> sure stands <sic>unparralled</sic> in the annals of<lb/> American congregations&#44; and its leaders are deser&#45;<lb/>ving of the severest censure.</p>
          <p rend="indent(1)">You state that probably you will be on<lb/> here about succoth&#44; I trust you may&#44; we<lb/> will all be pleased to see you and if<lb/> you come I hope that it may be your<lb/> pleasure to deliver a discourse at the<lb/> synagogue of <hi rend="underline">our</hi> congregation. I should<lb/> like you to let me know at what time<lb/> you will be on here&#44; exactly the day&#44;<lb/> you expect to arrive.</p>
		<pb n="2"/>
			<p>There is nothing of interest a stirring here<lb/> and must conclude in wishing that you<lb/> may be remembered in the Book&#45;of Life<lb/> and believe me to remain</p>
          <p rend="indent(6)">Your sincere friend</p>
          <p rend="indent(7)"><persName role="author">Jacob Ezekiel</persName></p>
			<p>Please remember me kindly to all my<lb/> old acquaintances and particularly to<lb/> <persName>Mrs Cozzens</persName> and her daughter&#44; and to <persName>Mrs<lb/> Hart</persName> &#38; Family.</p>
		<pb n="3"/>
			<p><addressee>Revd Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
          <p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
          <p rend="indent(2)"><placeName>Pa</placeName></p>
          
        </body>
